D. Acquisition Strategy
The Explosive Ordnance Disposal (EOD) Render Safe (RS) program utilizes existing government contract vehicles to acquire RS SKO Kits. C5ISR engineers provide
support for all RS SKO electronic countermeasure (ECM) components such as the MODI and newly developed AN PLT-6v1. DEVCOM AC provides engineering support
to the remaining RS SKO components and legacy EOD. PM-CCS will support C5ISR and DEVCOM AC efforts to stay informed on the latest technologies for the EOD
community. The program will continue to use the existing government contract vehicles for the production and deployment phase as well as to continue the assessment
of capabilities during technical refresh.




