Continue MOSA software development to support Laser Warning Receiver (LWR) integration, test and fielding efforts for ground
combat vehicles and enable future hard kill and soft kill active protection systems integration with the VBK. On Armored Multi-
Purpose Vehicle (AMPV) and Stryker, complete VBK with LWR integration through Critical Design Review. For Abrams and



