The JTNC will continue Joint Communications Marketplace (JCM) development and refinements to meet DoD and Industry
requirements in conjunction with DoD Instruction 4630.09. The JTNC will manage evolution of the JCM to provide value-added
collaborative environment tools, enabling Government and Industry to share information on innovative technologies and DoD
