PdM Waveforms is responsible for core activities, includes analyzing, developing, and updating legacy and current waveforms that operate on multiple radio sets
supporting network-centric operational warfare. Waveform developments (upgrading, developing, and maintaining) will generally be procured through full and open
contract competitions or through leveraging other government agencies.

