- Finalize design concept based on feasibility study
- Initiate technology design and demonstration phase with up to two vendors to begin 2nd interceptor development efforts
- Begin integration of 2nd interceptor with IBCS command and control and the IFPC Inc 2 launcher with up to two vendors

