D. Acquisition Strategy
PdM Robotic and Autonomous Systems (RAS) developed a Performance Specification (PSPEC) from the Enhanced Robotic Payloads-Unmanned Ground Systems
(ERP-UGS) Capability Development Document (CDD). PdM RAS released a request for proposal from industry on capabilities to meet the PSPEC which resulted in
the selection of the best capability to be further developed, integrated into the host platforms, and tested as a system in an Abbreviated Engineering Manufacturing
Development (EMD) phase. After a successful EMD, a production decision will be made to enter Production and Deployment (PD) phase.




