C. Accomplishments/Planned Programs ($ in Millions)                                                                             FY 2025      FY 2026      FY 2027
Title: Next-Gen OPIR GEO                                                                                                          458.727      422.173      485.703
Description: Development of the Next-Generation Overhead Persistent Infrared (Next-Gen OPIR) Geosynchronous Earth Orbit
